TITLE: NGINX Configuration for Flowise Reverse Proxy
DESCRIPTION: NGINX server block configuration to set up a reverse proxy for Flowise, allowing access via a custom domain without specifying the port.
SOURCE: https://github.com/flowiseai/flowisedocs/blob/main/esp/configuracion/deployment/aws.md#2025-04-18_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
server {
    listen 80;
    listen [::]:80;
    server_name yourdomain.com; #Example: demo.flowiseai.com
    location / {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:3000;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
        proxy_set_header Connection 'upgrade';
        proxy_cache_bypass $http_upgrade;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;
    }
}
```

